# AUDIO::GET_VEHICLE_DEFAULT_HORN

## Summary
Return the horn sound hash

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle

## Returns
* **INT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns hash of default vehicle horn

Hash is stored in audVehicleAudioEntity
